			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			Silk GIs are good items and look really monkish. To make them you'll need a high tailoring skill probably about 40+ could be more as I'm only making raw silk at the moment. The ingredients are Tunic pattern+3 silk swatches+2 heady Kiolas.<BR>
<BR>
silk swatches are made by combining 2 spider silks and heady kiolas are a brewing item make from 2kiola saps+water+empty bottle, you'll need a 30ish skill to make this at any consistency. good luck hope this helps.<BR>
<BR>
Takuan Soho (yoroshiku onegaishimasu)
